{"tid":569954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【冇品遊客】爬入龍門石窟喪擺pose影相 網民轟：中國人劣根性","createTime":"2018-02-23T07:39:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-23T07:42:43.000Z","uid":10958,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f9413e90bf00699a5d79d2901a27c697268b2fa7","tid":569954,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T07:39:50.000Z","msg":"<strong>【冇品遊客】爬入龍門石窟喪擺pose影相 網民轟：中國人劣根性</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180223&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=57864699\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180223%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D57864699&d=nGmPlKXyr6%2Bq9HMFUFVD5f%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=72b4ec3b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180223%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D57864699&h=a4e1d268\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180223&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=57864699</a><br />\n<br />\n農曆新年期間大批內地民眾湧到各個影點旅遊，河南洛陽的5A級景點龍門石窟，也是遊人如鯽，不過，有不少人竟私自翻過圍欄，爬入有逾1,500年歷史的洞窟內，搔首弄姿地拍照留念，引來網民撻伐：「甚麼原因導致中國人這個樣子呢？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180223/large/1519351277_fd5c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180223%2Flarge%2F1519351277_fd5c.jpg&h=0f0fa7d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現場影片顯示，在多個石窟裏都有遊客，他們站在石窟的邊緣，不斷擺姿勢，讓同伴拍攝。<br />\n景區工作人員稱，這些遊客都是違規爬進石窟，他們一直都在制止這些不文明行為，但農曆新年期間遊客眾多，一日有四、五萬人，「他們也是趁亂翻進去的」。<br />\n不少網民批評，這是「中國人的劣根性」，亦稱這些人破壞文物，應該「重罰吧，罰個傾家蕩產」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180223/57864699\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180223%2F57864699&d=nGmPlKXyr6%2Bq9HMFUFVD5f%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=4e236fae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180223%2F57864699&h=63915dbd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180223/57864699</a>"},{"pid":"d16134259d852cd2a7492d7443df483c17d5884c","tid":569954,"uid":79793,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T07:41:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed6a348189f52a045e691b813a1ce199f2c9cf0f","tid":569954,"uid":116530,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T07:42:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/154238_0e04155d58a3ccc1c533ac38404e31ca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F154238_0e04155d58a3ccc1c533ac38404e31ca.png&h=27d5c06e&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}